            <li><strong>Share Your Adventures:</strong> Post about your travels, college fests, tournaments, or even
                those spontaneous hangouts. From scenic photos to memorable stories, this is your canvas.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Our Vision</h3>
        <p>
            We aim to create a digital hub where the students of OUTR can come together to share their unique stories
            and experiences. Travel Diaries is not just about places - it's about moments, memories, and the connections
            we make along the way.
        </p>
        <p>
            So, whether you're backpacking through a scenic trail or cheering for your team at a tournament, let Travel
            Diaries be your go-to platform to document and share your journey.
        </p>
        <p>
